STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff,
v.
T.L., Defendant-Movant. M-186/187 September Term 2018
080664 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 18, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-187) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the petition for certification (M-186) is denied.
